Title: AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE MUNICIPALITY OF BONDO, PROVINCE OF TAYABAS, TO THAT OF-"AURORA."
Data:
[ Commonwealth Act No. 527, May 11, 1940 ]
AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE MUNICIPALITY OF BONDO, PROVINCE OF TAYABAS, TO THAT OF-"AURORA."
Be it enacted by the National Assembly of the Philippines:
Section 1. The name of the municipality of Bondo, Province of Tayabas, is changed to that of "Aurora."
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.ℒαwρhi৷
Approved, May 11, 1940.
